Aliza Gur https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aliza_Gur 0 Aliza Gur (Hebrew: עליזה גור‎; born Alizia Gross, 1 April 1940, Ramat Gan, Mandatory Palestine) is an Israeli actress who was Miss Israel of 1960 and a semifinalist in the Miss Universe pageant held in Miami Beach that same year. Her parents had fled Germany during Hitler's dictatorship and settled in Mandatory Palestine, where her brother and she were born.
